# ── Default: ignore everything, whitelist only what belongs in the repo ──
# Convention: place local-only tools (monitors, debug scripts, drafts) in `local/`.
# Anything under local/ is automatically excluded by the wildcard below.
*

# ── Whitelist: core project files ──
!.gitignore
!LICENSE
!README.md
!requirements.txt

# Source code
!src/
!src/**

# Essential pipeline scripts only
!scripts/
!scripts/generate_preview.py
!scripts/deploy_site.sh
!scripts/run_pipeline.sh
